remarks.para:
EnableOutlining property enables the outlining of text in EditControl.  It
            set True if outlining of the text in EditControl to be enabled ;
            otherwise, false. By default, it is set to true.

members.member:

            Get or set a value indicating whether Find And Replace Window has to be shown or not

            /// 
ShowFindAndReplace property returns the Visibility mode of Find And replace.



Set True if Find And Replace window has to be displayed;
            otherwise, False. By default, it is set to True.



XAML



<syncfusion:EditControl Name="EditControl1"
            ShowFindAndReplace="True">



C#



EditControl1.ShowFindAndReplace = True;

